OL,3,C'I had to tell my dad he had cancer':
OL,4,CSerious failings in deaf healthcare
OL,6,FThe daughter of a deaf man who died
OL,7,Ffrom cancer says his care was impacted
OL,8,Fby a severe lack of sign language
OL,9,Fprovision.
OL,11,FKate Boddy's father, who lived near
OL,12,FMold, was diagnosed with cancer in
OL,13,F2022, but when the NHS was unable to
OL,14,Fprovide a BSL interpreter, she was
OL,15,Fforced to deliver the news.
