OL,3,C'I had to tell my dad he had cancer':
OL,4,CSerious failings in deaf healthcare
OL,6,FThroughout his treatment, Kate says
OL,7,Fthe lack of provision also meant her
OL,8,Ffather was unable to connect with
OL,9,Fsupport groups or even access
OL,10,Fresources about his treatment.
OL,12,FKate said, "He was a proud deaf BSL
OL,13,Fuser.
OL,15,F"He was proud of his language, he had
OL,16,Flimited understanding of written and
OL,17,Fspoken British English because BSL is
OL,18,Fsuch a different language to English.
