OL,3,C'I had to tell my dad he had cancer':
OL,4,CSerious failings in deaf healthcare
OL,6,FA Royal National Institute for Deaf
OL,7,FPeople (RNID) report found that seven
OL,8,Fout of ten deaf people and people with
OL,9,Fhearing loss in Wales have never been
OL,10,Fasked about their communication needs
OL,11,Fwithin a healthcare setting.
OL,13,FThe report also found that almost one
OL,14,Fin ten people who are deaf or have
OL,15,Fhearing loss have avoided calling an
OL,16,Fambulance or attending A&E because of
OL,17,F"inaccessible communication".
OL,19,FMartin and his wife, Denise, are both
OL,20,Fdeaf and said they have faced the same
OL,21,Fissues in the healthcare system.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
