OL,3,C'I had to tell my dad he had cancer':
OL,4,CSerious failings in deaf healthcare
OL,6,F"It is really dangerous because even
OL,7,Fif families have the best of
OL,8,Fintentions, they are not qualified to
OL,9,Frelay that information, so people are
OL,10,Fcoming away from appointments confused
OL,11,Fand maybe missing out on really
OL,12,Fimportant treatment."
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government says it is
OL,15,F"reviewing the standards across
OL,16,Fhealthcare in Wales" and is "working
OL,17,Fwith organisations such as RNID and
OL,18,Fthe British Deaf Association".
